Package com.lukeleber.scandroid.interpreter.elm327 Description

Implementation details for the ELM327 can be found within this package. Refer to the OpCode class for more detailed information as to how to configure the ELM327 for use.

Otherwise, using the ELM327 implementation is very simple: 

     /// arbitrary communication interface
     CommunicationInterface comm = ...;

     /// single constructor
     ELM327 elm = new ELM327(comm);

     /// asynchronously start the interpreter
     elm.start();

     /// start talking with a vehicle
     elm.sendRequest(...);
